{"tid":449301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民激辯支付寶先進過八達通？方保僑：港人慣用八達通","createTime":"2017-10-27T05:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T02:29:39.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9445edd45e21b9418805c5af0636d1b221f16e","tid":449301,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"雖然很多人對支付寶的印象，都是内地研發的交易平台。然而，近年香港不少商戶都引入了支付寶作爲全新的交易方法。同樣作爲電子支付平台，很多人不禁會用八達通跟支付寶比較。雖然不少人認爲八達通更好用，但慢慢開始有人認爲支付寶比起八達通先進多了，認爲香港人應該嘗試接受科技帶來的進步。究竟在大家的心目中，是八達通比較先進，還是支付寶比較先進？<br />\n<br />\n有巴打在討論區出帖，討論八達通跟支付寶的優勢以及缺點。要知道，支付寳連接智能手機，就連香港都愈來愈多商戶接受支付寶付款，普及程度高。無論是大金額還是超小金額，都能夠透過支付寳付款，就像將信用卡、現金、EPS 等功能綜合在一起，有支付寶根本完全不用帶其他支付工具出街。然而，不少人卻寧願用八達通都依然不肯接受支付寶。<br />\n<br />\n有網民就認爲八達通勝在付款、增值都十分方便，支付寳要打開 QR code 才能夠使用認真麻煩。而且八達通不用上網都能夠使用，一來比較安全，二來就算手機沒有電都沒有影響。相反支付寶遇上手機沒有電的情況，就等於完全失效。另外，支付寶申請十分麻煩，要實名認證，有私隱的隱患。<br />\n<br />\n不過説到底，很多網民都認爲八達通雖然方便，然而八達通公司卻「不思進取」。如果八達通能夠輕鬆連接手機使用，又能夠令到小商戶、的士等商戶都肯接受八達通付款，大家根本就不需要考慮專用支付寶付款，所以錯的都是八達通公司。<br />\n<br />\n網民點睇八達通？<br />\n<br />\n優<br />\n<br />\n    快捷方便，商戶有裝機就一嘟付款<br />\n    現金、信用卡自動增值任選<br />\n    沒有必要連電話連網絡使用，較安全<br />\n    手機沒有電都用得<br />\n<br />\n缺<br />\n<br />\n    主要是面對面交易<br />\n    付款上限 HK $1000 太低<br />\n    推行多年，但很多商店不接受（例如的士）<br />\n<br />\n網民點睇支付寳？<br />\n<br />\n優<br />\n<br />\n    普及性高，部份街市都用到<br />\n    連接手機，商戶掃 QR code 就能使用<br />\n    擁有信用卡、EPS、現金多項付款功能<br />\n    面對面、遙距付款都支援<br />\n<br />\n缺<br />\n<br />\n    申請麻煩，要實名、付款要手續費<br />\n    付款步驟多<br />\n    手機沒有電變廢人"},{"pid":"a65c9466a09c7b4800cf385803f15e812a1caabb","tid":449301,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"網民對此的反應兩極，<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=68HAh7OoHQLeirTrrrI34gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=aa1779b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 就此訪問香港互動市務商會會長方保僑（Francis），他表示支付平台連接手機、網絡使用是大趨勢，雖然現階段支付寶領先一步，然而支付寶在香港的固定客比較少。相比之下，港人較習慣使用八達通，八達通公司近年亦大力整合「O! ePay」以及八達通手機 App，跟不同的商戶合作，相信不久的將來，亦能夠讓大家輕鬆透過手機用八達通進行支付吧！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1933399/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%BF%80%E8%BE%AF%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%AF%B6%E5%85%88%E9%80%B2%E9%81%8E%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%EF%BC%9F%E6%96%B9%E4%BF%9D%E5%83%91%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%85%A3%E7%94%A8%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1933399%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25BF%2580%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2594%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E5%2585%2588%25E9%2580%25B2%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2580%259A%25EF%25BC%259F%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%2583%2591%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2585%25A3%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2580%259A&d=68HAh7OoHQLeirTrrrI34gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=68ab2dcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1933399/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%BF%80%E8%BE%AF%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%AF%B6%E5%85%88%E9%80%B2%E9%81%8E%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%EF%BC%9F%E6%96%B9%E4%BF%9D%E5%83%91%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%85%A3%E7%94%A8%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A</a>"},{"pid":"1ab624184957e9639147c7cce3aae31d1a21048e","tid":449301,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>缺<br />\n<br />\n推行多年，但很多商店不接受（例如的士）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓? 乜的士接受支付寶咩？<br />\n<br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648e527ab6ef201773f2c8e07bfb0dfaf783f8ad","tid":449301,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>網民點睇支付寳？<br />\n<br />\n優<br />\n<br />\n普及性高，部份街市都用到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大把街市都用到八達通啦！<br />\n<br />\n寫文條友有無落過街市？"},{"pid":"4a697252e5e2c550a757c41ff9745b13ddb432e9","tid":449301,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>網民點睇支付寳？<br />\n<br />\n優<br />\n<br />\n擁有信用卡、EPS、現金多項付款功能</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫文條友真係ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 架喎<br />\n<br />\n八達通都有信用卡功能架<br />\n<br />\n你八達通用信用卡自動增值<br />\n<br />\n咪即係用信用卡經八達通比錢囉"},{"pid":"83d18717f003f4fb87c1d1506fbb3bd9203a34d5","tid":449301,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"乜有辯過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7948627464b084a0c9a1f90e8e089e6a9bf39fa4","tid":449301,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"Apple pay 呢屌"},{"pid":"049497745052bdcf2db2108dd933eb5f9c75e5a6","tid":449301,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"作者抄完就算"},{"pid":"b12cb1281d399c0de3358c98135dfa9e41268e69","tid":449301,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>網民點睇八達通？<br />\n<br />\n缺<br />\n<br />\n推行多年，但很多商店不接受（例如的士）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有的士係接受八達通架, 寫文條ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔做資料搜集, 左抄右抄<br />\n<br />\n如果我係腦細, 真係會扣佢年尾花紅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110719/photo/0719-00176-013b2.jpg?t=1509085098043\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20110719%2Fphoto%2F0719-00176-013b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1509085098043&h=c6c69c04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78914bf585afb0683ff4d912c89c1c847a56a5b7","tid":449301,"uid":63950,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7ef6c4aaf70558fab229b802333f1cfc1ef0e05","tid":449301,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作者抄完就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢真係上FORUM左抄右抄, 自己唔做research, 又唔verify d facts<br />\n<br />\n呢d妓者真係抄撚左佢費事勞氣"},{"pid":"008e6f6e13db90e6807518a2e12294c88ca60a85","tid":449301,"uid":63950,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eec6277691017f4b4bf9a4b6f3cab847e1632acb","tid":449301,"uid":26266,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"同8達通比，支能寶嘅優點竟然係普及性高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbeb4947560a74d805a719a08f12407c7dc78f0e","tid":449301,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>網民點睇八達通？<br />\n<br />\n缺<br />\n<br />\n推行多年，但很多商店不接受（例如的士）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有的士係接受八達通架, 寫文條ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔做資料搜集, 左抄右抄<br />\n<br />\n如果我係腦細, 真係會扣佢年尾花紅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110719/photo/0719-00176-013b2.jpg?t=1509085098043\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20110719%2Fphoto%2F0719-00176-013b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1509085098043&h=c6c69c04&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">科技領先10年</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n的士可用八達通   \t發佈日期： <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2006-06-28</span></span><br />\n<br />\n八達通自動繳費系統進軍的士，經過兩年研發，八達通解決了的士咪錶與八達通讀卡機分流的系統，市民將來乘搭的士可以「嘟」卡找數，毋須在下車前急急數錢。新界二十部的士率先試驗新系統，為期一至三個月，如系統運作良好，黃的士集團會在旗下的士引入自動收費系統，方便乘客及司機。不過，有的士司機擔心八達通系統會令乘客減少給小費，影響收入。 <br />\n<br />\n八達通卡有限公司銷售及市務總監鄭韓菊芳表示，系統可讓的士司機將咪錶金額輸入讀卡機內，乘客便可在車廂內的八達通讀卡機上確認金額，拍卡付費。但該系統暫不會在個別的士上安裝。該系統亦有額外解決小費的安排，若乘客有意給司機小費，可指示司機輸入較咪錶金額為高的車資，然後拍卡經電子系統付「貼士」。據介紹，系統亦特別設計了便利的士業租車的程序，向集團租用的士的司機，在開工前輸入私人密碼，電腦便會記錄每更營業額，結算後五至七天即可向司機發放收入。"},{"pid":"2c0c90163b49ff8bde06c463d0b5d1bd802060a5","tid":449301,"uid":77143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:27:06.000Z","msg":"支付寶唔興啦<br />\n宜家大陸人多數微信支付"},{"pid":"3e71df38182a4e752a71a5592b671efc893f36cb","tid":449301,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>網民點睇八達通？<br />\n<br />\n缺<br />\n<br />\n推行多年，但很多商店不接受（例如的士）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有的士係接受八達通架, 寫文條ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔做資料搜集, 左抄右抄<br />\n<br />\n如果我係腦細, 真係會扣佢年尾花紅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110719/photo/0719-00176-013b2.jpg?t=1509085098043\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20110719%2Fphoto%2F0719-00176-013b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1509085098043&h=c6c69c04&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">科技領先10年</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n的士可用八達通   \t發佈日期： <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2006-06-28</span></span><br />\n<br />\n八達通自動繳費系統進軍的士，經過兩年研發，八達通解決了的士咪錶與八達通讀卡機分流的系統，市民將來乘搭的士可以「嘟」卡找數，毋須在下車前急急數錢。新界二十部的士率先試驗新系統，為期一至三個月，如系統運作良好，黃的士集團會在旗下的士引入自動收費系統，方便乘客及司機。不過，有的士司機擔心八達通系統會令乘客減少給小費，影響收入。 <br />\n<br />\n八達通卡有限公司銷售及市務總監鄭韓菊芳表示，系統可讓的士司機將咪錶金額輸入讀卡機內，乘客便可在車廂內的八達通讀卡機上確認金額，拍卡付費。但該系統暫不會在個別的士上安裝。該系統亦有額外解決小費的安排，若乘客有意給司機小費，可指示司機輸入較咪錶金額為高的車資，然後拍卡經電子系統付「貼士」。據介紹，系統亦特別設計了便利的士業租車的程序，向集團租用的士的司機，在開工前輸入私人密碼，電腦便會記錄每更營業額，結算後五至七天即可向司機發放收入。</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">麥明詩下次可以電召八達通的士<br />\n<br />\n10年前已有, 唔駛勞氣</span></span>"},{"pid":"e11bf9ea714892dde782ef2e99e05c0700242d47","tid":449301,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>網民點睇八達通？<br />\n<br />\n缺<br />\n<br />\n推行多年，但很多商店不接受（例如的士）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有的士係接受八達通架, 寫文條ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔做資料搜集, 左抄右抄<br />\n<br />\n如果我係腦細, 真係會扣佢年尾花紅